1. On se **pokušao** udati za nju, ali nije uspio. (He tried to marry her, but he didn't succeed.)

2. Ona **pokušala** da ispuni njegove želje, ali nije uspela. (She tried to fulfill his wishes, but she didn't succeed.)

3. On je **pokušavao** da bude bolji, ali mu nije pošlo za rukom. (He was trying to be better, but he didn't succeed.)

4. Ona će se **pokušati** da završi zadatak što pre. (She will try to finish the task as soon as possible.)

5. Njegov sin se **pokušava** da se snađe u novoj školi. (His son is trying to find his way in the new school.)